name: Pluralsight d3 course
tagline: repo for playing with pluralsight d3 course
body:
### pluralsight d3 course
=====================

This project is an application/directory contains** my implementation code** of
pluralsight d3 tutorial videos.
Since the source code is not currently published,
and there is some guesswork and inaccuracies in some of the videos,
the correct, completely functional solutions are presented here.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
